room_title: Escape room "National Treasures" by Axxiom Escape Rooms Rehoboth in Rehoboth Beach
room_description: It will take an attention for detail or a knowledge of puzzle encryption to find your way through this Exodus. Built on the theme of our America’s past, this room has a great appreciation for our country’s history. We take you back to the seventeen and eighteen hundreds and challenge you through several eras of great historical occurrences.
